        "title": "ui(i18n): localize agents panels (overview and tools/skills) for zh-CN",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Problem: Agents page overview panel and tools/skills panel had hardcoded English strings when using Simplified Chinese locale.\n- Why it matters: Non-English users see English labels, tabs, buttons, and tool metadata in the agents page.\n- What changed: Extracted all hardcoded strings from `ui/src/ui/views/agents-panels-overview.ts` and `ui/src/ui/views/agents-panels-tools-skills.ts` into i18n keys, added translations to both `en.ts` and `zh-CN.ts`. Fixed duplicate `agents` object in `en.ts` that caused missing keys regression. Fixed `formatCountLabel` plural suffix for Chinese locale.\n- What did NOT change: No functional behavior, logic, or styling changed. No backend changes.\n\n## Change Type\n\n- [x] Chore/infra\n\n## Scope\n\n- [x] UI / DX\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n- Behavior or issue addressed: Agents page overview panel, tabs, tools/skills panel, and tool metadata were not localized to Simplified Chinese.\n- Real environment tested: Local dev gateway (`OPENCLAW_SKIP_CHANNELS=1 node scripts/run-node.mjs --dev gateway`).\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: Built UI assets with `pnpm ui:build`, started gateway, opened Control UI Agents tab, verified Overview, Files, Tools, Skills, Channels, and Cron tabs in Chinese.\n- Evidence after fix: Screenshot — agents page tabs render in Chinese (概览 / 文件 / 工具 / 技能 / 频道 / 定时任务). ![agents-overview-tab](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/git-jxj/openclaw/pr-assets-agents/.github/pr-assets/agents-overview-tab.png)\n- Observed result after fix: zh-CN locale shows fully translated agents panel UI.\n- What was not tested: Other non-English locales.\n\n## Root Cause\n\nN/A — not a bug fix.\n\n## Regression Test Plan\n\nN/A.\n\n## User-visible / Behavior Changes\n\n- Agents page overview panel now fully localized to Simplified Chinese (zh-CN).\n- Agents tools/skills panel now fully localized to Simplified Chinese.\n- English locale unchanged (new keys added, existing behavior preserved).\n\n## Security Impact\n\n- New permissions/capabilities? (No)\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? (No)\n- New/changed network calls? (No)\n- Command/tool execution surface changed? (No)\n- Data access scope changed? (No)\n\n## Repro + Verification\n\n### Environment\n\n- OS: macOS\n- Runtime: Node 22 (local dev)\n\n### Steps\n\n1. `pnpm ui:build` to build Control UI assets\n2. `OPENCLAW_SKIP_CHANNELS=1 node scripts/run-node.mjs --dev gateway` to start gateway\n3. Open Control UI in browser, navigate to Agents tab\n4. Switch locale to zh-CN\n5. Verify Overview, Tools, and Skills panels show Chinese text\n\n### Expected\n\n- Tab labels: 概览, 文件, 工具, 技能, 频道, 定时任务\n- Overview labels: 工作区, 主模型, 运行时, 技能筛选, 模型选择, 回退\n- Tools panel: 工具权限, 全部启用, 全部禁用, 当前可用, 快速预设\n- Tool counts: 4 工具, 4 已启用工具, 3 实时工具\n\n### Actual\n\n- All above verified locally.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- [x] Screenshot/recording\n\n**After — Agents Overview Tab**\n![agents-overview-tab](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/git-jxj/openclaw/pr-assets-agents/.github/pr-assets/agents-overview-tab.png)\n\n**After — Agents Page (Files Tab)**\n![agents-page](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/git-jxj/openclaw/pr-assets-agents/.github/pr-assets/agents-page-fixed.png)\n\n**After — Agents Tools Tab**\n![agents-tools](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/git-jxj/openclaw/pr-assets-agents/.github/pr-assets/agents-tools-final.png)\n\n## Human Verification\n\n- Verified scenarios: Agents tab overview panel, tools panel, skills panel in zh-CN locale.\n- Edge cases checked: English locale still renders correctly.\n- What was not verified: Other non-English locales.\n\n## Compatibility / Migration\n\n- Backward compatible? (Yes)\n- Config/env changes? (No)\n- Migration needed? (No)\n\n## Risks and Mitigations\n\nNone.",
